@startuml seq-tab-navigation
title Tab Navigation Flow

actor Child
participant "BottomTabBar" as TabBar
participant "Next.js Router" as Router
participant "ThemeProvider" as Theme
participant "Fastify API" as API
participant "Page Component" as Page

Child -> TabBar: Taps tab (e.g., Browse)
TabBar -> TabBar: Update activeTab state\nhighlight selected tab
TabBar -> Router: router.push(tab.route)

Router -> Theme: Read current AgeBandTheme
Theme --> Router: {ageBand, colors, fontSizes}

Router -> API: GET /content?ageBand={band}\n&category={tab context}
API --> Router: filtered content list

Router -> Page: Render page with data
Page -> Page: Apply theme CSS variables\n(colors, typography)
Page --> Child: Age-appropriate themed UI

@enduml
